  "description": "Single-pane health of an entire Linux fleet scraped by node_exporter: who is up, who is down, and the worst CPU, memory and disk pressure anywhere in the fleet — so on-call can triage hundreds of hosts in one glance instead of opening per-host dashboards one by one.",
